unpublishedAction.name: initializeRetainKPObject

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
        const retain_keyPersonData = {}
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ENTITY_TYPE = 'UBO Individual Person'
		   	retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_IS_AUTH_SIGN = false
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_OTHERS_INFO = ''
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PARTNER_PERC = Number(0).toString()
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FIRSTNAME = Input1.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MIDDLENAME = Input3.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_LASTNAME = Input4.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FATHERNAME = Input5.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_GENDER = Select4.selectedOptionValue
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DOB = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_NATIONALITY = Select3.selectedOptionValue
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_RES_TAX_PURPOSE = Select5.selectedOptionValue
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_GOVT_ID= Input18.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TAX_ID  = Input7.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_NO = Input19.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_EXPIRE_DATE = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DESIGNATION  = Input20.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_HOLD_PERC= Number(Input22.text).toString()
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_IS_POLITICALEXPOPER = Checkbox1.isChecked
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_IS_MINOR = vayUboMinorFlag.isChecked
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_GUARDIAN_NAME = Input21.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_UBO_GUARDIAN_RELATIONSHIP =Input8.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY = vayIndUboAddCountrySelect.selectedOptionValue
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE1  = Input9.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE2  = Input10.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY  = Input11.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_DISTRICT  = Input12.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE  = Input13.text
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_ZIP = Input15.text
        return retain_keyPersonData
    }
